import React from 'react';

const TableHeaders = () => (
  <tbody>
    <tr className="table-headers">
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Rotation Period</th>
      <th>Orbital Period</th>
      <th>Diameter</th>
      <th>Climate</th>
      <th>Gravity</th>
      <th>Terrain</th>
      <th>Surface Water</th>
      <th>Population</th>
      <th>Films</th>
      <th>Created</th>
      <th>Edited</th>
      <th>URL</th>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
);

export default TableHeaders;
